name: Cartoon Cat: The Return DEMO
description:
The "Threequel" to the FoxyMan1987 Cartoon Cat game Trilogy.

All characters belong to Trevor Henderson and Cartoon Cat model made by ludomcraft on deviantart. All other models and animations made by me.

How to Play: Press the left arrow key to go to the door. If cartoon Cat is there, press and hold space to keep the door closed. 1press the left arrow again to go back.
